OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with late sunshine, then long
OL,7,Fclear spells after sunset. Overnight
OL,8,Fdry with long clear spells and a few
OL,9,Fmist and fog patches, these mainly in
OL,10,Fthe east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny isolated mist and fog
OL,13,Fpatches will be quick clear leaving a
OL,14,Fdry day with light winds and
OL,15,Fpredominantly clear skies giving
OL,16,Fplenty of sunshine. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
