OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fsettled and warm Thursday and Friday
OL,7,Fwith variable cloud and plenty of
OL,8,Fsunny spells. A mostly cloudy day on
OL,9,FSaturday with showers possible.
OL,10,FBreezier on Thursday, otherwise light
OL,11,Fwinds.
